<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666666;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Password Changed</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= @resource.respond_to?(:name) && @resource.name.present? ? @resource.name : @resource.email %>!</p>

      <p>We're contacting you to notify you that your password has been changed successfully.</p>

      <p>If you did not change your password, please contact our support team immediately as your account may have been compromised.</p>

      <p>For security reasons, we recommend:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Using unique passwords for different accounts</li>
        <li>Changing your passwords regularly</li>
        <li>Never sharing your password with anyone</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @resource.email %>. If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Your App Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
